@startuml
title User Account Lifecycle - 3.9 (UserStatus)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #EEECFB
  BorderColor #8B7FD6
  FontColor #1A1A1A
  ArrowColor #444444
}
hide empty description

[*] --> ACTIVE : Account created & verified
ACTIVE --> LOCKED : Admin locks account\n(PATCH /api/admin/users/:id/status)
LOCKED --> ACTIVE : Admin unlocks account

ACTIVE : Can sign in and use the platform
LOCKED : Sign-in blocked\n(admin cannot lock own account)
@enduml
